    <div id="VerifySession">
        <h1>Session ID 登入驗證</h1>
        <hr>
        接口名稱：<code>VerifySession</code><br/>
        接口說明：使用 SessionID 取得登入帳號資訊<br/>
        參數列表：appId, session, uid, signature<br/>
        <table class="table table-striped">
            <col width="15%">
            <col width="85%">
            <tr>
                <th>參數名稱</th>
                <th>描述</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>appId</td>
                <td>Game key</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>session</td>
                <td>Login後可用<a href="#GetSessionID">GetSessionID()</a>取得</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>uid</td>
                <td>Login後可用<a href="#GetOpenID">GetOpenID()</a>取得</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>signature</td>
                <td>server返回的簽名</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        範例：
        <pre>SgSDK.Instance.VerifySession(appId: "app id", session: "session", uid: "uid", signature: "signature")</pre>
        返回值：
        <h4>Verify結構</h4>
        <table id="Verify" class="table table-striped">
            <col width="15%">
            <col width="85%">
            <tr>
                <th>參數名稱</th>
                <th>描述</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Code</td>
                <td>狀態代碼</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Msg</td>
                <td>狀態描述</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Account</td>
                <td>帳號</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>OpenID</td>
                <td>Open ID</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>EMail</td>
                <td>EMail</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    <br>
